name: User tries to click on the information overlay to see the info and closes it
description: User profile when there are no free liter transactions and also to check functionality of Free Liters Information Overlay
descriptionHtml: User profile when there are no free liter transactions and also to check functionality of Free Liters Information Overlay

testStage.description: User profile when there are no free liter transactions and also to check functionality of Free Liters Information Overlay

steps.name: I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I get the text "FREE LITERS HISTORY" from the Account Screen
I check that the application text: "FREE LITERS HISTORY" is equals to expected value: "FREE LITERS HISTORY"
I click on "FREE LITERS HISTORY" tab
I get the text "Free liters history" header on Free liters screen
I check that the application text: "Free liters history" is equals to expected value: "Free liters history"
I click on information Icon from Free liters screen
I get header text from information overlay
I check that the application text: "Total Free Liters" is equals to expected value: "Total Free Liters"
I get description text from information overlay

I check that the application text: "Get 1 free liter for every 50 liters you pump. Plus, play games to earn even more. Use your free liters at checkout!" is equals to expected value: "Get 1 free liter for every 50 liters you pump. Plus, play games to earn even more. Use your free liters at checkout!"

parameters.name: Actual:
parameters.value: Get 1 free liter for every 50 liters you pump. Plus, play games to earn even more. Use your free liters at checkout!

parameters.name: Expected:
parameters.value: Get 1 free liter for every 50 liters you pump. Plus, play games to earn even more. Use your free liters at checkout!

steps.name: I get text "OK" from information overlay
I check that the application text: "OK" is equals to expected value: "OK"
I click on "OK" button from information overlay
I check if Information overlay is closed
I click on information Icon from Free liters screen
I get header text from information overlay
I check that the application text: "Total Free Liters" is equals to expected value: "Total Free Liters"
I click on "Close" button
I check if Information overlay is closed
